reviewText: I ordered this ring because I needed something gold on my right hand to go with another ring. It's very pretty, just a bit too yellow. I still like it and will wear it when I need to balance out the gold.
i really like this ring, great for everyday or dressing up. it is a little thick but the gold looks very real in person. i already got one compliment on it.
Fits, is wearing well...looks good. Only things I would say is the gold is a little too bright/shiny for me.
Very pretty. Looks like the real thing. No one has ever asked if its real, they just assume it is and that it's worth a lot!

I wish I read the actual reviews when I put it on my wish list. Come to find out, you need to ORDER IT IN A LARGE SIZE!Once I purchased a larger size, it is beautiful! Excellent quality and matches well with my wedding rings.
